{
  "texts": [
    "This selection process was conducted in two stages.",
    "Initially, the first author, who has eight years of experience in teaching evidence-based medicine and bibliometric analysis, identified a preliminary set of 14 papers based on their titles and abstracts.",
    "Subsequently, all four authors collaboratively examined the shortlisted papers by reviewing the full texts.",
    "Potentially ambiguous cases were discussed among the authors to achieve consensus.",
    "This process yields five survey papers."
  ]
}